@DATABASE "Rambo"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - R - Rambo"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - R
                   ====================================

                                   Rambo
                                   =====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(27401,0) ZXAMPoke(27402,201) ZXAMPoke(60263,0)"}          27401,0:27402,0:60263,0
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38841,24)"}          38841,24

                         Note that the Immunity POKE does not always work when
                         you are in the chopper (like when fighting the Russian
                         chopper).

                         One slightly alarming thing was that the game crashed
                         once I had managed to destroy the Russian chopper. I
                         don't know if this is a bugged copy I have (from Speccy
                         Sensations 2), or the game is incompatible with the
                         emulator at that stage, or even if maybe the game's
                         programmer(s) have been clever and makes the game
                         reset if it detects a cheat at that stage (a fairly
                         simple check routine is all that would be needed)..

                         Oh, and was I the only one in the world who was crap 
                         at this game?

                         Rastan.
@endnode
